data.description: Nestled in Wylie’s sought after The Harvest neighborhood, this home was designed and crafted with detail. A modern farmhouse design with inviting entry welcomes guests inside! Open concept floorpan provides great functionality and includes a vaulted living room ceiling with exposed wood beam and fireplace that easily becomes the focal point of the room. Chef’s kitchen with gas cooking, plenty of cabinetry, walk-in pantry, and oversized kitchen island that provides plenty of prep space and bar style eating. The spilt floorpan design offers primary bed & bath privacy and boasts a spa like feel with the relaxing soaking tub, dual-vanity, stand-in shower, and walk-in closet. Your guests will have plenty of space with 3 additional bedrooms and a shared full bath. Work from home, this floor-plan delivers with a private office as well. Patio provides shade and a spot to have cookouts with friends and family. HOA to be established in 2024, covers grounds maintenance and community pool.
